      "variant": "main",
      "html": "<h4>Activity</h4>\n<p>Add the polynomial functions. Evaluate the sum for each given value.</p>\n<p>\\(z(x) = 8x^2 + 4x - 6\\)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; \\(w(x) = -5x^2 + 2x + 3\\)</p>\n<br>\n<!--Text Entry Interaction Start -->\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input\" data-button-text=\"Solution\" data-fire-event=\"eventShow\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\">\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-content\">\n<ol>\n<li>\\( (z + w)(x) = \\) ___________ </li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-prompt\">\n<p>Enter your answer here:</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-ack\">\n<p>Compare your answer:</p>\n<p>\\((z + w)(x) = 3x^2 + 6x - 3\\)</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!--Interaction End -->\n<br>\n<br>\n<!--Text Entry Interaction Start -->\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input\" data-button-text=\"Solution\" data-fire-event=\"eventShow\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\">\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-content\">\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>\\( (z + w)(6) = \\) ___________</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-prompt\">\n<p>Enter your answer here:</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-ack\">\n<p>Compare your answer:</p>\n<p>\\((z + w)(6) = 141\\)</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!--Interaction End -->\n<br>\n<br>\n<!--Text Entry Interaction Start -->\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input\" data-button-text=\"Solution\" data-fire-event=\"eventShow\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\">\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-content\">\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>\\((z + w)(-9) = \\) ___________</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-prompt\">\n<p>Enter your answer here:</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-ack\">\n<p>Compare your answer:</p>\n<p>\\((z + w)(-9) = 186\\)</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!--Interaction End -->\n<br>\n<br>\n<!--Text Entry Interaction Start -->\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input\" data-button-text=\"Solution\" data-fire-event=\"eventShow\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\">\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-content\">\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>\\((z + w)(0)\\) = ___________</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-prompt\">\n<p>Enter your answer here:</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-ack\">\n<p>Compare your answer:</p>\n<p>\\((z + w)(0) = -3\\)</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!--Interaction End -->\n<br>\n<p>Subtract the polynomial functions. Evaluate the sum for each given value.</p>\n<p>\\(m(x) = -6x^2 + 2x - 8\\)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; \\(n(x) = -x^2 - 7x - 6\\)</p>\n<br>\n<!--Text Entry Interaction Start -->\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input\" data-button-text=\"Solution\" data-fire-event=\"eventShow\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\">\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-content\">\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li>\\((m - n)(x) =\\) ___________ </li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-prompt\">\n<p>Enter your answer here:</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-ack\">\n<p>Compare your answer:</p>\n<p>\\((m - n)(x) = -5x^2 + 9x - 2\\)</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!--Interaction End -->\n<br>\n<br>\n<!--Text Entry Interaction Start -->\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input\" data-button-text=\"Solution\" data-fire-event=\"eventShow\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\">\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-content\">\n<ol start=\"6\">\n<li>\\((m - n)(-2) =\\) ___________ </li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-prompt\">\n<p>Enter your answer here:</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-ack\">\n<p>Compare your answer:</p>\n<p>\\((m - n)(-2) = -40\\)</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!--Interaction End -->\n<br>\n<br>\n<!--Text Entry Interaction Start -->\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input\" data-button-text=\"Solution\" data-fire-event=\"eventShow\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\">\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-content\">\n<ol start=\"7\">\n<li>\\( (m - n)(0) =\\) ___________</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-prompt\">\n<p>Enter your answer here:</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-ack\">\n<p>Compare your answer:</p>\n<p>\\((m - n)(0) = -2\\)</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!--Interaction End -->\n<br>\n<br>\n<!--Text Entry Interaction Start -->\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input\" data-button-text=\"Solution\" data-fire-event=\"eventShow\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\">\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-content\">\n<ol start=\"8\">\n<li>\\((m - n)(4) =\\) ___________</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-prompt\">\n<p>Enter your answer here:</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-ack\">\n<p>Compare your answer:</p>\n<p>\\((m - n)(4) = -46\\)</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!--Interaction End -->\n<br>\n<br>\n<!--Text Entry Interaction Start -->\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input\" data-button-text=\"Solution\" data-fire-event=\"eventShow\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\">\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-content\">\n<ol start=\"9\">\n<li>What is a good way to check that you found the correct sum or difference when adding or subtracting polynomial functions?</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-prompt\">\n<p>Enter your answer here:</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-ack\">\n<p>Compare your answer:</p>\n<p>Substitute a value for \\(x\\) into the individual polynomial functions. Add or subtract the results. The answer should be equal to the value you find when you substitute it into the sum or difference of the polynomial functions.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!--Interaction End -->\n<br>\n<h4>Video: Combining and Evaluating Polynomial Functions</h4>\n<p>Watch the following video to learn more about how to add and subtract polynomial functions and evaluate them at a given value:</p>\n<video controls=\"true\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" width=\"550\">\n<source src=\"https://k12.openstax.org/contents/raise/resources/eaecc03382b9de51eb04d6d681ab65c784d6e188\">\n<track default=\"true\" kind=\"captions\" label=\"On\" src=\"https://k12.openstax.org/contents/raise/resources/9ce97a7daeee9a7bec7f2554961f0695fb891989\" srclang=\"en_us\">https://k12.openstax.org/contents/raise/resources/eaecc03382b9de51eb04d6d681ab65c784d6e188\n    </video>"
